	(text "POWER ISOLATION STAGE\n* Takes the main +18V rail and converts it to a +/-15V isolated set of rails.\n* A common-mode choke is used to remove any unwanted common transients from the isolated rails.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.574 63.5 0)
